{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund AI training for all teachers",
        "additional_details": "AI can be a useful tool in education from Early Years to University. However, we believe that unless there is a unified standardised approach to AI usage, there could be misuse or a disparity in education delivery. In our view each student has a right to have access to AI and that can only be provided in the classroom.",
        "background": "Fund dedicated CPD training to teachers in AI, to allow them to use AI in the classroom and explain to their students best practice and use of AI.",
